Module nl.naturalis.common
Package nl.naturalis.common.collection

Interface IntList

All Superinterfaces:
Emptyable
All Known Implementing Classes:
IntArrayList
public sealed interface IntList extends Emptyable permits IntArrayList (not exhaustive)
The ubiquitous list-of-int class, while we await Valhalla. Note that IntList is a sealed interface with just two implementations: one (IntArrayList) allows mutations on the list and the other is immutable. Instances of the immutable variant can only be obtained through the static factory methods on this interface.

      void setCapacity(int newCapacity)
